      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Texas Incentives & Rebates</h2>
      
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Federal Incentives</h3>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-6 space-y-2">
        <li><strong>Solar Investment Tax Credit (ITC):</strong> 30% of total solar system cost (through 2032)</li>
        <li><strong>Energy Efficient Home Improvement Credit:</strong> Up to $1,200/year for HVAC upgrades</li>
